characterCustomizations.biography:
Hey! My name Is Drunk. I play a guardian druid in mythic+ keystones. I do not raid, nor am I in a raiding guild. A lot of people ask me WHY GUARDIAN? And I try to tell them all the same thing. Its something I just enjoy playing. I've played every tank class at end tier and really love the druid play-style and versatility that I can play other specs as well. Plus I feel I have to plan more in my pulls as a guardian then other tanks which is a great challenge for me in my opinion.

â€‹

I'm Always interested in running keys with friends, viewers or just other players. Feel free to swing by my stream anytime I'm live at twitch.tv/drunkentreegaming for Mid to High Tier Druid Game-play.
